name: Meautiful Busic
description: 1. Ce N’est Pas Un Jouet! 2. ATTENTION! 3. I Don't Play Around 4. Don't Make Me Laugh 5. Girls N Candy 6. LMS [Super-Hero Squad vocal mix] 7. Raw Riddim, Inc. (featuring MJay, Jai Michele & Curtis Khan) 8. MANIKSM PART I: Deep Sleep 9. Wanna See You Move 10. Girls N Candy Part 2 (featuring Dreams 2.5.) 11. ATTENTION! (LAGS remix) After years on the underground, rocking clubs & even the country's biggest festival, B.B. Manik finally releases his debut album. Showcasing his unique abilities, every single song on the album is freestyled! Featuring guest appearances from Curtis Khan, MJay & more, the album is blessed with production from Prepare To Meet Thy Broom!, LAGS (of Gallows) & even Manik himself! Albums don't get more exciting than this,so snap up a copy today & find out why so many fans "love his style"!

name: All Or Nowt
description: After a slew of classic mixtapes & a host of breath-taking shows, the UK's next big MC finally releases his official debut. Largely self-produced & featuring a range of styles & genres, this has to be heard to be believed. The witty & sharp flow of one the scene's top artists is matched only by his unique beats. 1.
